Class TextResourceCombo

              net.middell.combo.TextResourceCombo
All Implemented Interfaces:
InputSupplier<Reader>, Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<TextResource>, Collection<TextResource>, List<TextResource>, RandomAccess
public class TextResourceCombo
extends ArrayList<TextResource>
implements InputSupplier<Reader>

An ordered sequential combination of text-based resources.

Serves as a container for resources, exposes aggregated metadata and is usable as an input supplier of the joint contents in the contained resources.

Author:
Gregor Middell
